Work fine, thanks. The keygen instructions are a bit vague. Follow this instead:

1) Open Terminal
2) Type in “chmod +x” HIT SPACE, then drag the keygen file in, “hit RETURN”
3)Now the file should be in EXEC format.
4)Drag the file in to the terminal again, without typing anything else. “HIT RETURN”
5) Copy the serial that appears.

Finally got the key maker working..
For those who have problems, use this command:
Open terminal:
Type in:
sudo chmod +x (drag file into terminal)
Hit ENTER
The file should change to an exec, just drag it back again and enter it.

Anyways, here are some serials if ur lazy:

CF592-FPW12-0888Y-TQXQV-NFHE8 
YC5E2-07ED5-H8DFZ-R5NGX-P6AZA 
ZF5D8-68X54-M807P-MWQQG-PGKU6
